---
/**
 * SkipLink.astro — visually-hidden "skip to content" link for keyboard/AT
 * users. Inline styles preserved from the original (they existed in source).
 */
---
<a href="#main" class="skip-link" style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;top:0;background:#fff;color:#0F2A4A;padding:.75rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;z-index:200;">Skip to content</a>
